t=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">美国时尚集合店 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/need-supply-co-s-new-in-house-line-has-your-cool-girl-basics-covered/#\">Need Supply Co.  推出自家设计的春夏男女装系列</a>，黑白色调为主的简约设计：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215405284YoHbqpK3WTMFzN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154053SQORzetL7ow2CBdl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154053vDUNrg0QtGYOkfc7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154054GsPcjx3NLQMu8wYp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154054bgYE2dHc7rznqs84.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}